HEADWORD: Top-boots
<hw>Top"-boots</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <def>High boots,
having generally a band of some kind of light-colored leather around the
upper part of the leg; riding boots.</def>⟦br⟧
